comments: Claxton (BKN) is established in a screening position when he collapses his arm and absorbs the oncoming contact.
Williams (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position when he absorbs the contact from Schroder (BKN) at the end of the drive.
Agbaji (TOR) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he moves to imminently guard an opponent.
Claxton (BKN) gathers the pass on his right foot and then legally begins his dribble.
Williams (TOR) initiates contact with Claxton's (BKN) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Schroder (BKN) briefly engages and disengages with Quickley (TOR) as the contact that occurs off-ball is marginal.
Johnson (BKN) is moving alongside Quickley's (TOR) path and marginal body contact occurs during Quickley's drive.
Claxton (BKN) cleanly blocks Williams' (TOR) shot attempt before the ball touches the backboard.
Schroder (BKN) establishes himself in Quickley's (TOR) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Quickley (TOR) legally contests Thomas' (BKN) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Claxton (BKN) makes clean contact to the ball as marginal contact occurs with Williams (TOR) during the rebound.
Thomas (BKN) contests the jump shot attempt and marginal lower body contact occurs with Quickley (TOR) as he returns to the floor.
Thomas (BKN) gives a step of distance when establishing himself in Williams' (TOR) path as he absorbs the marginal contact during the screen.
Quickley (TOR) extends his forearm into Schroder's (BKN) body, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Thomas (BKN) is moving alongside Quickley's (TOR) path and the body contact that occurs as they come together at the start of the drive is marginal.
Thomas (BKN) cleanly deflects the loose ball away from Temple (TOR).
Temple (TOR) and Claxton (BKN) come together as they pursue the loose ball and marginal contact occurs.
Nwora (TOR) cleanly dislodges the ball away from Schroder (BKN). Any arm contact that occurs after the dislodge is deemed incidental.
Schroder (BKN) regains possession of the loose ball when he signals for a timeout, which he is awarded.
Temple (TOR) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Clowney (BKN) as the steal occurs.
Clowney (BKN) jumps alongside Temple's (TOR) path and cleanly blocks the driving shot attempt.
Clowney (BKN) cleanly blocks Temple's (TOR) shot attempt before the ball touches the backboard.
Quickley (TOR) moves into Schroder's (BK) path and he initiates body contact that affects Schroder's SQBR.
Schroder (BKN) brushes Quickley's (TOR) off-arm as the contact does not affect Quickley's SQBR.
After communicating with the Replay Center, it is determined that Claxton (BKN) makes contact with the ball after it hits the backboard and has a chance to score.
Dick (TOR) brushes Schroder's (BKN) arm and marginal contact occurs.
Quickley (TOR) commits a take foul on Schroder (BKN).
Quickley (TOR) establishes himself in Wilson's (BKN) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Quickley (TOR) brings his hands toward Schroder (BKN) and releases as the screen is set, which does not affect Schroder's ability to defend.
